data.description: A TOTAL hidden gem. Enjoy all of the luxuries & conveniences of city living w/ a spacious back yard of a suburban home; minutes from Willmore & Carondelet park! This 3 bed 2.5 bath home w/ over 1,500 sqft is ready for you to call home! Spacious front entry foyer w/ a potential formal dining area & front sitting area greet you as you walk in. Entertain in the HUGE Alleyway Kitchen w/ TONS of cabinet & counter space featuring newer cabinetry, tile back splash, recessed lighting, some newer appliances & tiled flooring. TWO full tiled bathrooms throughout the main floor. Just off the kitchen, spacious mud room or utility room w/ access to the back yard. Big master bedroom & 2 spacious bedrooms provide ample living space for your extra guest this holiday season. Partially finished basement w/ 1/2 bath & access to the tuck under 2 car garage and partially finished bsmt. Don't forget the HUGE (almost) completely fenced in back yard w/ dog kennel.  Ring in the new year at 4640 Oldenburg Ave!
